Download Phython
Open the cmd prompt, type python and click enter to check the version
Set the environment variables  and make sure 2 python is available (python and scripts)


Download Pycharm for IDE

select new project
select new environment as  virtualenv
select the base intrepretor ur python version
select inherit global site packages

navigate to the project path using copy path from project folder in pycharm through cmd prompt
type : pip3 install selenium

must include this line(from selenium import webdriver) at each .py file
can be execute from terminal using command python xxx.py(Navigate to the .py file path)

for firefox, desired capabilitiy must be added

to see/generate compiler file(.pyc) type = python -m py_compile filename.py
to execute the class file =  python filename.py

